videos.headline: Blasingame opens game with 65-yard Vanderbilt TD
videos.description: Kyle Shurmur completes a pass to Khari Blasingame who turns on the jets to score a 65-yard Vanderbilt touchdown up the sideline.

videos.headline: Lovett scores 12-yard Baylor TD
videos.description: John Levitt takes the handoff 12 yards to the end zone to allow Baylor to take a 10-7 lead over Vanderbilt.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt answers Baylor with 68-yard TD
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaughn takes off 68 yards to score a Vanderbilt touchdown to put them back on top of Baylor 14-10.

videos.headline: Hasty hustles 18 yards for the score
videos.description: JaMycal Hasty carries the ball 18 yards for a Baylor touchdown to end the 1st quarter.

videos.headline: Vaughn runs 69 yards for second TD
videos.description: Ke'Shawn Vaughn scores his second rushing touchdown of the night after zipping 69 yards downfield.

videos.headline: Baylor's Martin shanks 25-yard kick
videos.description: Connor Martin turns his ankle and falls awkwardly as he shanks the 25-yard Baylor field goal.

videos.headline: Baylor's Ebnerer shakes 3 defenders to score 34-yard TD
videos.description: Trestan Ebner slips through the defense and makes two defenders collide to score a 34-yard Baylor touchdown.

videos.headline: Brewer powers in TD from a yard out
videos.description: Baylor's Charlier Brewer bulldozes his way into the end zone to score and increase the Baylor lead over Vanderbilt to 31-21.

videos.headline: Blasingame scores second touchdown
videos.description: Khari Blasingame takes the handoff 2 yards for the Vanderbilt touchdown.

videos.headline: Vanderbilt defense comes up with wild INT
videos.description: Vanderbilt's Randall Haynie comes up with an interception on Baylor's Charlie Brewer in the back of the end zone for a touchback as the pass was juggled.

videos.headline: Blasingame muscles his way for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Khari Blasingame scores his third touchdown of the night by pushing the pile across the plane.

videos.headline: Brewer connects with Ebner for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Charlie Brewer finds Trestan Ebner who scores a big-time 75-yard touchdown to put Baylor back in the lead over Vanderbilt 38-35.
